caption: This von's chicken is awesome! people are very kind and I tried other von's chickens which are different location, this location was the best taste! I strongly recommend here to get yummy healthier chicken! you can park on street easily to pick up your food too.
Awesome service, delicious chicken without all that heavy batter allowing more flavor. 4 star since I didn't get  the onions.  Rice cakes are very tasty soft not too chewy!

(Translated by Google) Terrible work ethics It really shines. Employment was canceled because a family member agreed to help the day before the first day of work. The next day, he made a call and told him to work again because of a problem. It's a place where people ridicule and play around is amazing. Parking was not available, so on full-time working days, they picked up before and after work. You only make $10 (and you have to pay tax), but the conclusion is that even on a day of making $50 a day, you have to ride the bus for 1 hour (different from the initial promise). There is no politeness. This is the best chicken ever. More over, the customer service is outstanding.  They treat you like family here. I can and will absolutely recommend this place.  My girlfriends an I just love everything on the menu and I know you will too. Go here but just know... It is addictive.

We dropped by the first time in this location today(Nuuanu), the owner’s are very friendly, they gave a free soda to us and offering to sit while waiting. Didn’t expect that. I recommend this location very nice people. Thank you so much for having a care with your customers. We really appreciate for your kindness.
Great delicious chicken! Very friendly owners. Easy street parking during  pandemic
